  "texts": [
    "Under these agreements, a significant portion or the entirety of the publisher's content becomes openly accessible to readers without paywalls.",
    "Additionally, many of these agreements cover the cost for authors at their institution to publish their work in open access formats without additional APCs.",
    "However, transformative agreements require institutions to allocate significant funds for these deals.",
    "The costs associated with these agreements may strain institutional budgets, particularly for smaller or underfunded institutions.",
    "Additionally, the uncertainty about long-term costs and sustainability poses a challenge, as the financial models for these agreements might evolve over time, potentially affecting institutions' ability to maintain participation."
